European Stocks Pare Earlier Losses as Shares of Mining Companies Advance

-- B y   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 
2011-05-16T15:06:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-16/european-stocks-pare-earlier-losses-as-shares-of-mining-companies-advance.html
European stocks pared their decline
as mining companies rallied. The Stoxx Europe 600 Index slipped
less than 0.1 percent to 280.3 at 4:05 p.m. in  London , having
earlier lost as much as 0.9 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
